creator: William Patten
description:
LibriVox recording of Junior Classics Volume 5: Stories That Never Grow Old by William Patten.

Read in English by Lynne Thompson; thestorygirl; Scott Snowman; Pooja DSr; ; Denise Nordell; rookieblue; TribalElder; Drew Johnson; Mike Pelton; Brett G. Hirsch; Tereza; Ellen Preckel; Larry Wilson; Teddy; Gary; Claire Schreuder; Lucretia B.; Matt Lusher; and Allie Cingi.

A selection of famous tales selected and re-worked for a junior audience. Stories are taken from Arabian Nights, Robinson Crusoe, Gulliver's Travels, Shakespearean plays, Pilgrim's Progress, Ivanhoe, and The Startling Adventures Of Baron Munchausen. (Summary by Lynne Thompson )

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
